      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CROCODILE ROLL (5) ran good time (22.51) winning a Grade 5 at Gawler when jumping from this same box. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. OSPREY CHRONOS (1) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 5.5 lengths (17.12) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Other over 300m. Hard to beat again. MAJESTIC MCLAREN (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Angle Park behind Carry On Kim (31.50) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to feature again. PRIME VOLTAGE (3) has claims fresh from a recent placing.",
